metadata.name: Transcend
metadata.description:
Transcend is a wonderful word that means rise above or leave behind.  I have risen above a lot of pain and difficulty in my life.  I have left behind evil.  I have not always left behind the emotional scars and I certainly haven't left behind the financial cost of freedom.  That's why I focus on transcending every day.  Present tense.  Today I transcend.


The iconic Sydney Opera House captured at dawn under a magnificent sky and the thinnest sliver of a moon is a reminder to amaze, to offer shelter to little ones, and to be unexpected and beautiful.  Each day is a new beginning and an opportunity to be grateful, to grow, and to build a brighter future.  Today I hope you will transcend too.


Burn 2 Transcends --> Redeem 1 Kindly Quokka  
If you want one of each: Buy 3 Transcends, Burn 2 of them.
